Usage: report_gates [-help] [-hinst <hInst>] [-out_file <string>]
                    [-sort {name count area leakage_power internal_power total_power switching_power}] [-power  | -leakage_power ]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <hInst>     # Name of the hinst to collect cell information. Only cell
                   # in the specified hinst will be considered ((hInst), optional)
-leakage_power     # Provide leakage power statistic only. (bool, optional)
-out_file <string> # File in which report will be saved into. If not specified,
                   # information only dumped into log. (string, optional)
-power             # Provide internal, switching, leakage and total power
                   # statistic. (bool, optional)
-sort {name count area leakage_power internal_power total_power switching_power}
                   # Param used to sort content of the tables to generate
                   # leakage_power/internal_power value only respected if the
                   # option -power is also specified. (enum, optional)